{"author":{"id":"783b610f274a0d93f6239db0fc75d0982606c877a4661d3aea84b42bc3a85cea"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1515543727,"nonce":"NZFoO3egVmp8dM+GL1iIuBp9Bzo=","metadata":{"github-id":"MDU6SXNzdWUyODcyNzU2MTI=","github-url":"https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/issues/1662","origin":"github"},"title":"BEDTools NucBed 2.27.0.0 fails when -pattern is used without -C","message":"**Tool**: NucBed profile the nucleotide content of intervals in a FASTA file (Galaxy Version 2.26.0.0)\n\n**MTS**: https://toolshed.g2.bx.psu.edu/view/iuc/bedtools/a8eabd2838f6\n\n**Problem**: Defaults and all other combinations of parameters work fine, except when using `-pattern` as `yes` and `-C` as `no`. See test histories below for error details.\n\n**Example that fails**:\n```\nbedtools nuc   -pattern  -fi '/data/1/galaxy_db/files/005/593/dataset_5593043.dat' -bed '/data/1/galaxy_db/files/005/593/dataset_5593044.dat' \u003e '/data/dnb01/galaxy_db/files/005/593/dataset_5593045.dat'\n```\n\u003cimg width=\"622\" alt=\"screen shot 2018-01-09 at 4 08 06 pm\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8999735/34749825-69148f20-f558-11e7-937d-70d08f3592ce.png\"\u003e\n\n**Example that passes**:\n```\nbedtools nuc   -pattern -C -fi '/data/1/galaxy_db/files/005/593/dataset_5593043.dat' -bed '/data/1/galaxy_db/files/005/593/dataset_5593044.dat' \u003e '/data/1/galaxy_db/files/005/593/dataset_5593049.dat'\n```\n\u003cimg width=\"632\" alt=\"screen shot 2018-01-09 at 4 07 41 pm\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8999735/34749857-b1bcb180-f558-11e7-889a-3c495fee3377.png\"\u003e\n\n**Test histories**:\n - https://usegalaxy.org/u/jen/h/bedtools-nucbed-test-history\n - https://galaxy.uni-freiburg.de/u/jenj/h/bedtools-nucbed-test-history-2\n\n**Minor**: Param typo `Igore case when matching -pattern` should be fixed to be `Ignore` when the correction is made. Use this or add in as new PR: https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/pull/1663","files":null}]}